    "### Measure 2: Dynamical Divisibility\n",
    "\n",
    "A process is **CP-divisible** (Markovian) if it can be written as:\n",
    "$$\\mathcal{E}_{t,0} = \\mathcal{E}_{t,s} \\circ \\mathcal{E}_{s,0}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "where each $\\mathcal{E}_{t,s}$ is completely positive.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Non-Markovian**: Cannot be factorized into CP maps."
   ]
